Naku, nagseselos ako.

444
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,560
Ang astig mo talaga.

445
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:09,520
Sikat ka na ngayon, Ko Song.

446
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:11,560
Magkita tayo mamaya.

447
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:18,320
Maghiwa-hiwalay na tayo. Kailangan kong mag-ensayo ng basketball.

448
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:19,960
Achi, sasama ka ba?

449
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:20,560
Mm.

450
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:22,000
Paano naman ako?

451
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,240
Sige, ayusin mo na ang love letter mo.

452
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:27,440
Ano ba 'to?

453
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:30,720
Iniwan na lang talaga nila ako nang basta-basta.

454
00:35:34,160 --> 00:35:34,680
Anong problema?

455
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:38,440
Inaantok na ako.

456
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:40,880
Hikab!

